(26, 'CCMN 15 Phương Mai', '1605461745cc.jpg', 4, 2, '15 Phương Mai, Đống Đa, Hà Nội', '<p>CCMN cho thu&ecirc; c&oacute; thể đến ở ngay</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vị trí siêu đắc địa: Sát Bệnh Viện Bạch Mai, Lão Khoa, Da Liễu, và các bv khác, 3 bước chân ra đến chợ và thiên đường ăn vặt, Tụ điểm của Đại Học Y, ĐH Bách Khoa, Kinh Tế, Xây Dựng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nội thất cơ bản (điều h&ograve;a, n&oacute;ng lạnh, giường tủ)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://scontent.fhan2-5.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/124825644_1272282166504468_8042817238200947590_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=JVSBBgdGzFsAX8Bw2gE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhan2-5.fna&amp;oh=ded28e8021c091a43cb32b2b69e5e061&amp;oe=5FD71308\" style=\"height:1280px; width:960px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://scontent.fhan2-4.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/125295200_1272282203171131_5045790266786618925_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=2E4cH5Q7rusAX-9g_AW&amp;_nc_oc=AQmL1jKnsKYfjWUb4DDdn9U3DgnbQNLZia8DnRsAD5VAv1RNrx8HhhkpZ6OVJCRs_-E&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhan2-4.fna&amp;oh=d7feea06c50c26800a218836770be9b5&amp;oe=5FD81786\" style=\"height:1280px; width:960px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://scontent.fhan2-6.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/125569292_1272282529837765_1377122322619009267_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=dnNKfmly5EUAX9cFh_A&amp;_nc_oc=AQkm6h5tK4ioJ4vuziyK2FO2cT4VX1nLBdGL7dno76P99nnsIcggvhetmSV-K1H_IX0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhan2-6.fna&amp;oh=7dda379c233d36606a6474d414c73a01&amp;oe=5FD6054A\" style=\"height:1280px; width:960px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://scontent.fhan2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/125225093_1272282766504408_690705173544678589_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=UokXwTVpLgMAX_rOLev&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhan2-1.fna&amp;oh=fde9b7e35d2d6391e493831338520c38&amp;oe=5FD86B3C\" style=\"height:1280px; width:960px\" /></p>\r\n', 35, 0, 0, 'có, kín', 'có, thông với phòng khách, ngủ', 1, 1, 'điện 3,5k/s